%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Hindutva%20Card%20is%20Not%20Working%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Poll-Bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151156%2F374943054_878995983596801_1036847113504325148_n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPredictably%20enough%2C%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20brought%20in%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20the%20campaign%20for%20the%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20toured%20the%20state%20for%20three%20days%20from%20October%2028%2C%20mocked%20the%20Congress%20for%20having%20doubted%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20intention%20to%20build%20the%20temple%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Chhindwara%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20date%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%20has%20been%20fixed%2C%20and%20asked%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20what%20do%20you%20have%20to%20say%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20barb.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20has%20raised%20objection%20to%20the%20BJP%20using%20photographs%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20its%20posters%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhopal%2Frow-over-bjps-ram-mandir-poll-posters-cong-complains-to-ec%2Farticleshow%2F104810517.cms%5C%22%3E%20filed%20a%20complaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERam%20temple%20billboards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBillboards%20and%20posters%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20built%20in%20Ayodhya%20have%20been%20put%20up%20by%20the%20BJP%20across%20the%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20posters%20announce%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBhavya%20Ram%20Mandir%20bankar%20ho%20raha%20hai%20taiyyar%2C%20fir%20iss%20baar%20BJP%20Sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(A%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20is%20being%20readied%2C%20this%20time%20again%20there%20will%20be%20a%20BJP%20government).%E2%80%9D%20It%20may%20not%20have%20been%20a%20coincidence%20that%20the%20posters%20suddenly%20sprung%20up%20in%20the%20state%20during%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20three-day%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20it%20not%20resonating%20with%20people%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20expectation%2C%20its%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20whip%20up%20religious%20fervour%20among%20the%20voters%20in%20the%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20around%20the%20Ram%20temple%20has%20evoked%20a%20sense%20of%20d%C3%A9j%C3%A0%20vu.%20The%20issue%20is%20not%20resonating%20with%20the%20electorate.%20Nor%20has%20it%20charged%20up%20the%20party%20cadres%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20too%20confused%20and%20dismayed%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-infighting-state-elections%5C%22%3Einfighting%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20tickets%20for%20constituencies%20to%20get%20nostalgic%20about%20the%20three-decade-long%20Ram%20Janambhoomi%20movement%20that%20culminated%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%20650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-629759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20for%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20played%20up%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinsult%E2%80%9D%20to%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20by%20harping%20over%20the%20controversial%20comment%20of%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%5C%22%3EUdhayanidhi%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20linking%20it%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20view%20by%20citing%20the%20two%20parties%E2%80%99%20association%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20(public%20blessings)%20rallies%2C%20the%20BJP%20played%20the%20Hindutva%20card%2C%20focusing%20its%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20controversy.%20On%20September%2014%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20trying%20to%20destroy%20Sanatan%20Dharma.%20The%20BJP%20has%20also%20been%20highlighting%20its%20development%20of%20religious%20tourist%20circuits%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Mahakal%20Lok%20corridor%20in%20Ujjain%20and%20the%20Adi%20Shankaracharya%20statue%20in%20Omkareshwar.%20But%20the%20electorates%20don%E2%80%99t%20appear%20impressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-bjp-shivraj-singh-chouhan-centre%5C%22%3EWith%20a%20Split%20House%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20MP%2C%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20Is%20Fighting%20for%20Himself%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apparent%20indifference%20among%20voters%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20galvanise%20them%20around%20the%20tried%20and%20tested%20Hindutva%20pitch%20is%20not%20surprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFour%20factors%20behind%20apparent%20apathy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20observers%20attribute%20the%20apathy%20to%20mainly%20four%20factors.%20One%2C%20the%20secular%20issues%20such%20as%20unemployment%2C%20price-rise%20and%20corruption%20are%20too%20overarching%20ones%20in%20this%20election%20to%20be%20subsumed%20by%20communal%20politics.%20The%20Congress%20is%20staying%20focused%20on%20these%20issues%2C%20sensing%20support%20to%20the%20party%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20promise%20for%20caste%20census%20has%20revived%20the%20Mandal%20versus%20Kamandal%20narrative%2C%20causing%20Other%20Backward%20Castes%20to%20priotise%20caste%20above%20religion.%20Caste%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20more%20dominant%20issue%20in%20this%20election.%20Both%20the%20main%20parties%20have%20been%20pretty%20sensitive%20to%20the%20narrative%20and%20allotted%20more%20than%2027%25%20seats%20to%20the%20OBCs%20who%20account%20for%20nearly%2050%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20Muslims%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20too%20few%20and%20too%20scattered%20for%20majoritarian%20triumphalism%20on%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20their%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFourth%20%E2%80%93%20and%20arguably%20the%20most%20important%20factor%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20astute%2C%20if%20controversial%2C%20strategy%20to%20neutralise%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20by%20deploying%20the%20rival%E2%80%99s%20religious%20symbolism%20with%20equal%20vigour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20divert%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20away%20from%20anti-incumbency%20sentiments%20against%20the%20state%20government%20is%20proving%20ineffective.%20But%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20left%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20push%20through%20its%20core%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20its%20ploys%20such%20as%20invisibilising%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20the%20last%2018%20years%2C%20sole%20focus%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20achievements%2C%20deployment%20of%20seven%20MPs%20including%20three%20union%20ministers%20and%20centralising%20the%20campaign%20have%20failed%20to%20brighten%20up%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20opinion%20polls%20had%20forecast%20Congress%20victory%20over%20the%20BJP%20with%20a%20slim%20margin.%20The%20latest%20opinion%20poll%20conducted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsdayexpress.com%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-survey-after-rebellion-put-bjp-in-tension-inflation-is-the-biggest-issue-in-the-elections%2F%5C%22%3EZee-C4%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20forecast%20132-146%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%2084-98%20seats%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20remarkably%2C%20the%20opinion%20poll%20has%20predicted%2046%25%20vote%20share%20to%20the%20Congress%20against%2043%25%20to%20the%20BJP.%20This%20survey%20was%20done%20after%20the%20battle%20lines%20had%20been%20drawn%20and%20candidates%20for%20both%20parties%20had%20been%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20neutralising%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20match%20the%20BJP%20in%20liberally%20flaunting%20religious%20symbolism%20was%20frown%20upon%20by%20a%20section%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20has%20proved%20effective%20in%20blunting%20the%20opponent%E2%80%99s%20edge%20on%20Hindutva.%20The%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20has%20tactfully%20ensured%20that%20the%20BJP%20oft-repeated%20claim%20in%20the%20past%20about%20the%20Congress%20being%20anti-Hindu%20sounded%20incredible%2C%20at%20least%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151458%2F367384106_900743161408994_2449008609315507060_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151458%2F367384106_900743161408994_2449008609315507060_n.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151458%2F367384106_900743161408994_2449008609315507060_n-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151458%2F367384106_900743161408994_2449008609315507060_n-683x1024.jpeg%20683w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FKamal%20Nath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENath%20has%20worn%20his%20Hinduness%20on%20his%20sleeve.%20He%20has%20often%20reacted%20to%20the%20charge%20of%20practising%20soft-hindutva%20by%20asking%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CKya%20BJP%20ne%20hindutva%20ka%20theka%20le%20rakha%20hai%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Can%20only%20the%20BJP%20practise%20Hindutva%3F)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20proudly%20declares%20himself%20a%20devotee%20of%20Lord%20Hanuman%20and%20has%20built%20a%20101-foot%20statue%20of%20the%20deity%20in%20Chhindwara.%20He%20courted%20controversy%20when%20he%20hosted%20Dhirendra%20Shastri%2C%20the%2027-year-old%20head%20priest%20of%20the%20Bageshwar%20Dham%2C%20at%20a%20religious%20event%20in%20Chhindwara%2C%20and%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20sync%20with%20Shastri%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20The%20PCC%20chief%20also%20hosted%20a%20religious%20event%20for%20another%20controversial%20Katha%20vachak%20Pandit%20Pradeep%20Mishra%20who%20too%20subscribes%20to%20and%20openly%20favours%20establishment%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-in-quest-for-power-is-congress-ready-to-compromise-on-secularism%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3A%20In%20Quest%20for%20Power%2C%20Is%20Congress%20Ready%20to%20Compromise%20on%20Secularism%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20party%20is%20carrying%20out%20such%20an%20experiment%2C%20where%20it%20wants%20to%20project%20itself%20as%20a%20better%20Hindu%20compared%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20experiment%20seems%20to%20be%20working%20well%20for%20the%20Congress.%20It%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20portray%20the%20Congress%20anti-Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20war%20of%20words%20has%20erupted%20between%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20leaders%20over%20the%20posters%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCongress%20has%20complained%20to%20the%20EC%20that%20Lord%20Rama%E2%80%99s%20temple%20photos%20and%20hoardings%20are%20being%20installed%20and%20should%20be%20brought%20down.%20Sometimes%20they%20call%20Lord%20Ram%20imaginary.%20This%20country%20cannot%20run%20without%20Lord%20Ram.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20reaction%2C%20Congress%20stalwart%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20said%20that%20he%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20Hindu%E2%80%9D%20and%20has%20donated%20more%20money%20than%20chief%20minister%20Chouhan%20to%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20But%20the%20use%20of%20religion%20in%20elections%20is%20barred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Ram%20mandir%20the%20temple%20of%20BJP%3F%20It%20is%20the%20temple%20of%20every%20person%20of%20this%20country.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20replica%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20and%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20Ram%20temple%20is%20being%20constructed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20three%20Diwali%20claim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Mandir%20took%20centre%20stage%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20after%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20state%20is%20set%20to%20celebrate%20Diwali%20festival%20thrice%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Diwali%2C%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20state%20poll%20results%2C%20and%20when%20the%20temple%20is%20inaugurated%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20230-member%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2017%2C%20with%20the%20vote%20count%20taking%20place%20on%20December%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698665444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151156%2F374943054_878995983596801_1036847113504325148_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-bjps-hindutva-campaign-is-not-working-in-madhya-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20match%20the%20BJP%20in%20liberally%20flaunting%20religious%20symbolism%20was%20frown%20upon%20by%20a%20section%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20has%20proved%20effective%20in%20blunting%20the%20opponent's%20edge%20on%20Hindutva.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-bjps-hindutva-campaign-is-not-working-in-madhya-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Deal%20With%20Visual%20Misinformation%20Circulating%20in%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F13095447%2FIMG_0163.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20three%20weeks%20since%20war%20began%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20social%20media%20has%20been%20taken%20over%20with%20images%20and%20stories%20of%20attacks%2C%20many%20of%20which%20proved%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20within%20hours%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20surprise%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F10%2F10%2F1204755129%2Fvideo-game-clips-and-old-videos-are-flooding-social-media-about-israel-and-gaza%5C%22%3Escreen%20grabs%20from%20a%20popular%20video%20game%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20shared%20by%20thousands%20of%20social%20media%20users%20as%20if%20depicting%20real%20scenes%20of%20violence%20against%20Israeli%20troops%20in%20Gaza.%20Five%20days%20later%2C%20a%20real%20explosion%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2F1207173798%2Ffake-accounts-old-videos-and-rumors-fuel-chaos-around-gaza-hospital-explosion%5C%22%3Espurred%20further%20sharing%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20such%20spurious%20images%20to%20buttress%20various%20claims%20and%20counterclaims%20about%20responsibility%20for%20the%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20this%20war.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20international%20commissions%20and%20tribunals%20working%20to%20mediate%20conflicts%20in%20Syria%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20elsewhere%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justsecurity.org%2F80404%2Fthe-intl-criminal-courts-ukraine-investigation-a-test-case-for-user-generated-evidence%2F%5C%22%3Ehave%20struggled%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20verify%20the%20large%20amount%20of%20digital%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholar.google.com%2Fcitations%3Fuser%3D7bfZyk8AAAAJ%26hl%3Den%5C%22%3Ehuman%20rights%20scholar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%2C%20of%20late%2C%20been%20studying%20the%20ethics%20of%20viewing%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20war%20and%20atrocities%20in%20situations%20where%20falsification%20of%20imagery%20is%20widespread.%20A%20principal%20lesson%20of%20this%20research%20is%20that%20users%20of%20social%20media%20have%20significant%20power%20to%20influence%20the%20content%20they%20receive%20and%20thus%20bear%20some%20responsibility%20when%20they%20consume%20and%20share%20false%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefining%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EScholars%20and%20policymakers%20distinguish%20misinformation%20from%20disinformation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.international.gc.ca%2Fworld-monde%2Fissues_development-enjeux_developpement%2Fresponse_conflict-reponse_conflits%2Fcrisis-crises%2Fukraine-disinfo-desinfo.aspx%3Flang%3Deng%23a1%5C%22%3Ebased%20on%20the%20intentions%20behind%20their%20creation%20and%20circulation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Misinformation%20consists%20of%20false%20information%20that%20is%20not%20created%20or%20circulated%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20deceive.%20Disinformation%20consists%20of%20false%20information%2C%20including%20visual%20information%2C%20that%20is%20intended%20to%20deceive%20and%20do%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20any%20war%2C%20misinformation%20proliferates.%20Rumors%20that%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20had%20fled%20Kyiv%20spread%20quickly%20after%20Russian%20forces%20invaded%20that%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fukraines-zelenskyy-squashes-rumors-hes-fled-kyiv-video-we-are-here-1682830%5C%22%3Eonly%20to%20be%20rebutted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20videos%20posted%20from%20the%20streets%20of%20the%20capital.%20The%20difficulty%20of%20sifting%20reports%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20along%20with%20the%20reality%20that%20Zelenskyy%20was%20personally%20at%20risk%2C%20made%20many%20people%20accept%20and%20share%20those%20rumors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20however%2C%20false%20information%20about%20conflicts%20comes%20from%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20governments%2C%20military%20officials%2C%20separatist%20groups%20or%20private%20citizens%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.icrc.org%2Flaw-and-policy%2F2021%2F03%2F30%2Ffog-of-war-and-information%2F%5C%22%3Eintentionally%20using%20texts%20and%20images%20to%20deceive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20Myanmar%2C%20for%20example%2C%20military%20propaganda%20officers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2018%2Faug%2F31%2Fmyanmar-army-fakes-photos-and-history-in-sinister-rewrite-of-rohingya-crisis%5C%22%3Epublished%20photographs%3C%2Fa%3E%20supposedly%20depicting%20Rohingya%20people%20arriving%20in%20the%20country%20under%20British%20colonial%20rule%20in%20the%20mid-20th%20century.%20In%20actuality%2C%20these%20photographs%2C%20shared%20to%20support%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20the%20Rohingya%20had%20no%20right%20to%20live%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20depicted%20refugees%20from%20the%201994%20Rwandan%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConditions%20for%20ethical%20responsibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20social%20media%20becomes%20saturated%20with%20falsified%20images%20of%20mass%20violence%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20other%20regions%20of%20the%20globe%2C%20individuals%20should%20ask%20what%20ethical%20responsibility%20they%20bear%20for%20their%20consumption%20of%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20might%20deny%20that%20users%20of%20digital%20media%20bear%20any%20such%20responsibility%2C%20since%20they%20are%20merely%20the%20passive%20recipients%20of%20content%20created%20by%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhilosopher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.princeton.edu%2Fpeople%2Fgideon-rosen%5C%22%3EGideon%20Rosen%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F3840937%5C%22%3Eclaims%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20when%20people%20are%20passive%20toward%20some%20occurrence%2C%20they%20generally%20don%E2%80%99t%20bear%20ethical%20responsibility%20for%20it.%20Anyone%20scrolling%20the%20internet%20will%20passively%20encounter%20hundreds%20of%20images%20and%20related%20texts%2C%20and%20it%20is%20tempting%20to%20assume%20they%20bear%20no%20responsibility%20for%20the%20images%20of%20war%20and%20mass%20violence%20that%20they%20see%20but%20only%20for%20how%20they%20respond%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20users%20of%20digital%20media%20are%20not%20merely%20passive%20recipients%20of%20falsified%20images%20and%20stories.%20Instead%2C%20they%20have%20power%20to%20influence%20the%20kinds%20of%20images%20that%20show%20up%20on%20their%20screens.%20This%20means%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20that%20users%20bear%20some%20ethical%20responsibility%20for%20their%20consumption%20of%20visual%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlgorithms%20and%20influence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDigital%20media%20platforms%20deliver%20content%20to%20users%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20complex%20decision-making%20procedures%20known%20as%20algorithms.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hachettebookgroup.com%2Ftitles%2Fshoshana-zuboff%2Fthe-age-of-surveillance-capitalism%2F9781610395694%2F%3Flens%3Dpublicaffairs%5C%22%3EThrough%20both%20online%20and%20offline%20behaviors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20users%20help%20determine%20what%20these%20algorithms%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20helpful%20to%20distinguish%20between%20influence%20and%20control.%20Having%20control%20over%20content%20would%20mean%20either%20encountering%20only%20images%20and%20stories%20that%20one%20consciously%20chooses%20or%20having%20the%20power%20to%20screen%20out%20any%20and%20all%20unwanted%20images.%20It%20is%20typical%20of%20digital%20communications%2C%20as%20philosopher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.some.ox.ac.uk%2Feminent%2Fonora-oneill%2F%5C%22%3EOnora%20O%E2%80%99Neill%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1017%2F9781108981583%5C%22%3Epointed%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20users%20lack%20the%20ability%20to%20control%20content%20in%20these%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20users%20can%20significantly%20influence%20the%20material%20they%20encounter%20in%20digital%20spaces.%20The%20algorithms%20by%20which%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20other%20digital%20networks%20deliver%20content%20to%20users%20are%20not%20fully%20transparent%2C%20but%20neither%20are%20they%20wholly%20mysterious.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20they%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fct%2Farticle-abstract%2F26%2F3%2F309%2F4061231%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext%5C%22%3Epropelled%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20users%E2%80%99%20past%20engagement%20with%20a%20platform%E2%80%99s%20content%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fact%20reflected%20in%20the%20very%20name%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CFor%20You%E2%80%9D%20page%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELiking%2C%20tagging%2C%20commenting%20on%20or%20merely%20continuing%20to%20watch%20images%20of%20war%20and%20atrocities%20tends%20to%20lead%20to%20additional%20encounters%20with%20such%20content.%20The%20potential%20risks%20of%20this%20algorithmic%20process%20became%20apparent%20in%20the%20mid-2010s%2C%20when%20YouTube%E2%80%99s%20algorithm%20was%20found%20to%20be%20leading%20users%20into%20progressively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2Fbusiness%2Fyoutube-terrorism.html%5C%22%3Emore%20extreme%20videos%20related%20to%20jihadist%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20major%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20community%20guidelines%20prohibiting%20incitement%20to%20violence%20and%20sharing%20of%20graphic%20content%2C%20those%20prohibitions%20are%20difficult%20to%20enforce.%20In%20the%20context%20of%20some%20ongoing%20wars%2C%20they%20have%20even%20been%20relaxed%20%E2%80%93%20with%20Facebook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fexclusive-facebook-instagram-temporarily-allow-calls-violence-against-russians-2022-03-10%2F%5C%22%3Etemporarily%20allowing%3C%2Fa%3E%20posts%20calling%20for%20violence%20against%20Russian%20troops%20and%20paramilitary%20groups%20occupying%20parts%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20for%20example.%20Taken%20together%2C%20these%20processes%20and%20policies%20have%20opened%20the%20door%20to%20substantial%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation%20about%20armed%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHiding%2C%20reporting%20or%20simply%20disengaging%20with%20violent%20content%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20tends%20to%20lead%20to%20fewer%20such%20messages%20coming%20in.%20It%20may%20also%20reduce%20the%20odds%20that%20such%20content%20will%20reach%20others.%20If%20one%20knows%20that%20a%20Facebook%20friend%20or%20TikTok%20content%20creator%20has%20shared%20false%20information%20before%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20block%20that%20friend%20or%20unfollow%20that%20creator.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20users%20have%20these%20means%20of%20influencing%20the%20images%20they%20receive%2C%20it%20is%20reasonable%20to%20assign%20them%20some%20responsibility%20for%20algorithmically%20generated%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVerifying%20images%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAltering%20patterns%20of%20engagement%20with%20digital%20content%20can%20decrease%20users%E2%80%99%20exposure%20to%20misinformation%20in%20wartime.%20But%20how%20can%20users%20verify%20the%20images%20they%20do%20receive%20before%20directing%20others%20to%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20simple%20protocol%2C%20promoted%20by%20educators%20and%20public%20health%20groups%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fguides.lib.uchicago.edu%2Fc.php%3Fg%3D1241077%26p%3D9082322%5C%22%3Eknown%20by%20the%20acronym%20SIFT%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20stop%2C%20investigate%2C%20find%2C%20trace.%20The%20four%20stages%20of%20this%20protocol%20ask%20users%20to%20stop%2C%20investigate%20the%20source%20of%20a%20message%2C%20find%20better%20coverage%2C%20and%20trace%20quotes%20and%20claims%20back%20to%20their%20original%20contexts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImages%2C%20like%20quotes%2C%20can%20often%20be%20traced%20to%20their%20original%20contexts.%20Google%20makes%20available%20its%20reverse%20image%20search%20tool%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewslit.org%2Ftips-tools%2Fdoctored-images%2F%5C%22%3Eallows%20users%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20select%20an%20image%20%E2%80%93%20or%20parts%20of%20it%20%E2%80%93%20and%20find%20where%20else%20it%20appears%20online.%20I%20found%20this%20tool%20helpful%20during%20the%20first%20months%20of%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20when%20Holocaust%20photographs%20were%20circulated%20online%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkansas-newspaper-cartoon-face-mask-holocaust-the-anderson-county-review-2020-7%5C%22%3Eposts%20comparing%3C%2Fa%3E%20mask%20mandates%20to%20deportation%20trains.%20Of%20course%2C%20as%20journalists%20and%20forensic%20researchers%20are%20quick%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freutersinstitute.politics.ox.ac.uk%2Fnews%2Fbbc-expert-debunking-israel-hamas-war-visuals-volume-misinformation-twitter-was-beyond%5C%22%3Epoint%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20tools%20can%20only%20be%20applied%20to%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20the%20images%20we%20encounter%20in%20our%20daily%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20technique%20or%20protocol%20will%20give%20users%20absolute%20control%20of%20the%20images%20they%20see%20in%20wartime%20or%20provide%20complete%20assurance%20against%20sharing%20false%20information.%20But%20by%20understanding%20users%E2%80%99%20power%20to%20influence%20content%2C%20it%20may%20be%20possible%20to%20mitigate%20these%20risks%20and%20promote%20a%20more%20truthful%20future.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F216059%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fpaul-morrow-911275%5C%22%3EPaul%20Morrow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Human%20Rights%20Fellow%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Funiversity-of-dayton-1726%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Dayton%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20