eat%20sadness%20that%20we%20announce%20the%20death%20of%20my%20sister%2C%20Shani%20Nicole%20Z.L.%20%5Bmay%20her%20memory%20be%20a%20blessing%5D%2C%20who%20was%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20at%20the%20party%20massacre%20in%20Re%E2%80%99im.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Foreign%20Ministry%20said%20that%20Shani%20Louk%E2%80%99s%20body%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cfound%20and%20identified.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20confirmation%20from%20the%20German%20Foreign%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShani%20Louk%20went%20missing%20after%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShani%20Louk%20went%20missing%20while%20attending%20the%20Supernova%20music%20festival%20in%20southern%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-at-war%2Ft-57547294%5C%22%3EIsrael%20that%20came%20under%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20Hamas%20militants%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20terror%20attacks%2C%20pictures%20and%20videos%20shared%20online%20showed%20a%20young%20woman%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20Shani%2C%20lying%20face%20down%20in%20a%20pick-up%20truck%20driven%20by%20militants.%20It%20was%20unclear%20from%20the%20footage%20whether%20she%20was%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20family%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20they%20had%20information%20she%20had%20been%20critically%20injured%20but%20was%20receiving%20treatment%20in%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20militants%20killed%20at%20least%201%2C400%20people%20during%20their%20assault%20on%20Israeli%20communities%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border.%20They%20also%20took%20at%20least%20229%20people%20hostage%2C%20including%20several%20Germans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20others%20are%20unaccounted%20for%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Israeli%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShani%20Louk%20