India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20Friday%2C%20October%2027%2C%20Stephan%20and%20I%20participated%20in%20a%20civil%20disobedience%20action%20in%20New%20York%20City%20calling%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20apparently%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20largest%20since%20the%20Iraq%20war.%20Several%20thousand%20people%2C%20mostly%20Jews%2C%20took%20over%20the%20Grand%20Concourse%20in%20Grand%20Central%20Station%2C%20and%20many%20more%20protested%20outside%20when%20the%20doors%20were%20locked.%20Though%20we%20have%20been%20activists%20our%20whole%20lives%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20we%20decided%20that%20the%20carnage%20underway%20in%20Gaza%2C%20funded%20by%20our%20tax%20dollars%2C%20and%20with%20no%20end%20in%20sight%2C%20required%20us%20to%20do%20more.%20We%20decided%20to%20partake%20in%20an%20action%20of%20civil%20disobedience%20and%20be%20among%20the%20several%20hundred%20that%20got%20arrested%20that%20night.%20It%20was%20seven%20hours%20of%20discomfort%2C%20but%20the%20pain%20of%20tight%20zip-tie%20handcuffs%20behind%20our%20backs%2C%20not%20being%20able%20to%20stretch%2C%20not%20being%20able%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom%2C%20the%20knowledge%20that%20there%20would%20be%20court%20dates%20afterwards%20and%20possible%20trouble%20with%20international%20travel%2C%20none%20of%20this%20seemed%20significant%20in%20the%20face%20of%2010%2C000%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinians%20dead%20and%20the%20death-count%20rising.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20action%20was%20organised%20by%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%20with%20support%20from%20IfNotNow%20and%20Jews%20for%20Racial%20and%20Economic%20Justice%2C%20all%20progressive%20and%20anti-Zionist%20Jewish%20organisations.%20It%20was%20profound%20and%20overwhelming%20to%20be%20a%20lone%20Hindu%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20thousands%20of%20Jews%20expressing%20their%20pain%20for%20the%20atrocities%20being%20committed%20in%20their%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-jewish-voice-for-peace-apartheid%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20in%20Our%20Name%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Jews%20Who%20Refuse%20to%20Be%20Bystanders%20to%20Historic%20Injustice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20person%20of%20conscience%20or%20faith%20can%20accept%20the%20carpet%20bombing%20of%20children%2C%20babies%2C%20innocent%20civilians.%20No%20person%20of%20conscience%20can%20accept%20communal%20punishment.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20unequivocally%20condemn%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20attack%20that%20occurred%20on%20October%207th%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Erefuse%20to%20respond%20to%20an%20atrocity%20with%20another%20atrocity%20even%20larger.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20chants%20that%20echoed%20through%20Grand%20Central%20Station%20was%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%20again%20for%20anyone%2C%20never%20again%20is%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20This%2C%20for%20us%2C%20is%20the%20most%20basic%20lesson%20of%20the%20Holocaust%20that%20many%20Jews%20seem%20to%20have%20forgotten.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20pain%20as%20a%20Hindu%20has%20been%20that%20Hinduism%20has%20been%20hijacked%20by%20Hindu%20supremacists%2C%20led%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Adityanath.%20They%20are%20entrenching%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20with%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20victimhood%20and%20danger%20from%20our%20Muslim%20siblings%2C%20and%20increasing%20Islamophobic%20sentiment.%20Under%20the%20current%20regime%2C%20India%20is%20being%20transformed%20into%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(nation)%20where%20Muslims%20and%20other%20religious%20minorities%20are%20neither%20welcome%20nor%20safe.%20Protesting%20with%20thousands%20of%20Jews%20calling%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20made%20me%20dream%20of%20a%20day%20when%20thousands%20%E2%80%93%20or%20even%20hundreds%20%