ousands%20of%20years%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20recent%20climate-related%20extremes%20mentioned%20in%20the%20paper%20that%20Huq%20co-authored%20are%20the%20heavy%20monsoonal%20rains%20that%20caused%20flash%20floods%20and%20landslides%20in%20northern%20India%20that%20killed%20more%20than%20100%20people%20in%20July%202023.%20%E2%80%9CClimate%20change%20is%20likely%20making%20monsoons%20in%20this%20region%20more%20variable%2C%20causing%20frequent%20landslides%20and%20floods%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20authors%20wrote%20in%20the%20paper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20paper%20serves%20as%20a%20scary%20warning.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20scientists%2C%20we%20are%20increasingly%20being%20asked%20to%20tell%20the%20public%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20crises%20we%20face%20in%20simple%20and%20direct%20terms%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20authors%2C%20including%20Huq%2C%20wrote.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%20is%20that%20we%20are%20shocked%20by%20the%20ferocity%20of%20the%20extreme%20weather%20events%20in%202023.%20We%20are%20afraid%20of%20the%20uncharted%20territory%20that%20we%20have%20now%20entered.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20September%2024%20this%20year%2C%2015%2C484%20scientists%20are%20signatory%20to%20the%20warning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHuge%20loss%20for%20Global%20South%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENumerous%20climate%20experts%20and%20officials%20have%20expressed%20shock%20at%20his%20death%2C%20and%20for%20the%20loss%20this%20means%20to%20the%20climate%20science%20discourse%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20Global%20South.%20Huq%20was%20among%20the%20many%20climate%20experts%20who%20had%20been%20instrumental%20in%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20historic%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20fund%20at%20the%20last%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20at%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland%20(COP27).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fnews-and-stories%2Fstory%2Fwhat-you-need-know-about-cop27-loss-and-damage-fund%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUN%20Evironment%20Programme%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20loss%20and%20damage%20%E2%80%9Crefers%20to%20the%20negative%20consequences%20that%20arise%20from%20the%20unavoidable%20risks%20of%20climate%20change%E2%80%9D%2C%20from%20rising%20sea%20levels%20to%20extreme%20weather%20events%20such%20as%20heatwaves%20and%20intense%20bouts%20of%20rainfall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeveloping%20countries%2C%20including%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%2C%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20climate%20change%20due%20to%20the%20increasing%20intensity%20of%20such%20events%20made%20more%20likely%20by%20climate%20change.%20The%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20aims%20to%20finance%20climate%20change%20mitigation%20and%20adaptation%20in%20developing%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20emotional%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fharjeet11%2Fstatus%2F1718621283376640272%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Harjeet%20Singh%2C%20head%20of%20global%20political%20strategy%20with%20Climate%20Action%20Network%20International%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Chard%20to%20grasp%E2%80%9D%20that%20Huq%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20at%20COP28%2C%20especially%20when%20he%20had%20attended%20all%2027%20preceding%20COPs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTogether%2C%20we%20fought%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund.%20The%20battle%20for%20climate%20justice%20remains%20ongoing%E2%80%A6I%20pledge%20to%20redouble%20my%20efforts%2C%20to%20uphold%20the%20torch%2C%20and%20to%20champion%20the%20cause%20with%20even%20more%20passion%20and%20hard%20work.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20do%20this%20in%20honour%20of%20your%20legacy%2C%20feeling%20your%20guidance%20and%20blessings%20from%20the%20heavens%20above%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fharjeet11%2Fstatus%2F1718621283376640272%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHuq%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpioneering%20global%20voice%20on%20adaptation%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20his%20%E2%80%9Cunwavering%20advocacy%20for%20loss%20and%20damage%20finance%E2%80%9D%2C%20were%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20a%20few%20of%20the%20many%20accomplishments%20that%20will%20forever%20be%20etched%20in%20our%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20huge%20loss%20to%20the%20Climate%20community%20and%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Faditimukherji%2Fstatus%2F1718629891954840036%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Aditi%20Mukherji%2C%20Director%2C%20Climate%20Change%20Impact%20Platform%20(CGIAR).%20%E2%80%9CMay%20he%20rest%20in%20peace%2C%20and%20May%20everyone%20else%20follow%20his%20legacy%20and%20make%20loss%20and%20damage%20funds%20a%20reality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20shocked.%20Saleem%20has%20been%20a%20driving%20force%20for%20climate%20justice%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20climate%20debate.%20His%20brilliant%20mind%2C%20ability%20to%20say%20what%20has%20to%20be%20said%20and%20dogged%20determination%20have%20been%20beacons%20for%20decades.%20I%20will%20miss%20him%20terribly%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fclimatemorgan%2Fstatus%2F1718501706667868176%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Jennifer%20Morgan%2C%20State%20Secretary%20and%20Special%20Envoy%20for%20International%20Climate%20Action%2C%20Federal%20Foreign%20Office%20of%20Germany.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fobituary-saleemul-huq-climate-voice-of-the-global-south-92528%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecent%20interview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Huq%20gave%20to%20climate%20journalist%20Jayanta%20Basu%2C%20he%20had%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Chopeful%20that%20COP28%20will%20deliver%2C%20including%20in%20key%20areas%20of%20adaptation%20and%20loss%20and%20damage%20which%20are%20so%20much%20important%20for%20South%20Asian%20countries%20including%20areas%20like%20the%20Sundarbans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698660052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30140910%2FF9japPsaMAAH-Ev.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fclimate-science-expert-saleemul-huq-passes-away-at-71%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Huq%20was%20a%20leading%20voice%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20in%20the%20international%20climate%20discourse%20and%20had%20played%20an%20instrumental%20role%20in%20furthering%20the%20cause%20of%20climate%20justice.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fclimate-science-expert-saleemul-huq-passes-away-at-71%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Till%20Death%20Palestine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14144837%2FF8Ujv0qWkAA5W3q.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20death%20instinct%20is%20ravaging%20the%20land%20of%20Palestine%20and%20massacring%20its%20inhabitants.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hamas%20commandos%2C%20trapped%20with%20two%20million%20refugees%20in%20what%20has%20been%20called%20an%20%E2%80%9Copen-air%20prison%E2%80%9D%2C%20had%20gone%20underground%20and%20prepared%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20receiving%20support%20from%20other%20regional%20powers%20and%20benefiting%20from%20a%20certain%20complacency%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Israel%2C%20which%20saw%20them%20as%20its%20%E2%80%9Cfavourite%20enemy%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20succeeded%20in%20launching%20an%20offensive%20which%20surprised%20Tsahal%20(Israel%E2%80%99s%20defense%20forces)%2C%20which%20was%20busy%20lending%20a%20hand%20to%20the%20Jewish%20settlers%20on%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20this%20understandably%20aroused%20the%20enthusiasm%20of%20Palestinian%20youth%20and%20opinion%20in%20the%20Arab%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExcept%20that%20it%20has%20been%20accompanied%20by%20particularly%20odious%20crimes%20against%20the%20Israeli%20population%3A%20the%20murder%20of%20adults%20and%20children%2C%20torture%2C%20rape%20and%20kidnapping.%20Such%20crimes%20can%20never%20be%20excused%20by%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20cause%20they%20claim%20to%20represent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20vagueness%20of%20the%20expression%2C%20they%20justify%20the%20use%20of%20the%20term%20terrorism%2C%20not%20only%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20actions%20themselves%2C%20but%20also%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20armed%20resistance%20organisation%20that%20plans%20them.%20There%20is%20more%3A%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20aim%20was%20not%20to%20provoke%20a%20response%20of%20such%20violence%20that%20the%20war%20would%20enter%20a%20new%2C%20truly%20%E2%80%9Cextermination-ist%E2%80%9D%20phase%2C%20obliterating%20forever%20the%20possibilities%20of%20the%20two%20peoples%20living%20together.%20And%20that%20is%20what%20is%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20is%20happening%20because%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20officially%20redefined%20in%202018%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnation-state%20of%20the%20Jewish%20people%E2%80%9D%2C%20has%20never%20had%20any%20political%20project%20other%20than%20the%20annihilation%20or%20subjugation%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20by%20various%20means%3A%20deportation%2C%20expropriation%2C%20persecution%2C%20assassination%2C%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-india-forsakerole-voice-of-moderation%5C%22%3EIsrael-Palestine%20Conflict%3A%20Why%20Has%20India%20Forsaken%20Its%20Role%20as%20a%20Voice%20of%20Moderation%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20sufficient%20to%20look%20at%20the%20map%20of%20the%20successive%20settlements%20since%201967%20for%20the%20process%20to%20become%20absolutely%20clear.%20After%20former%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minster%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EYitzhak%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERabin%E2%80%99s%20assassination*%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0the%20governments%20that%20signed%20the%20Oslo%20Accords%20did%20not%20conclude%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-state%20solution%E2%80%9D%20should%20be%20implemented%2C%20preferring%20instead%20to%20tame%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20and%20cordon%20off%20the%20West%20Bank%20with%20checkpoints.%20And%20now%20that%20a%20racist%20right-wing%20has%20taken%20over%2C%20it%20is%20pure%20and%20simple%20ethnic%20cleansing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20%E2%80%9Crevenge%E2%80%9D%20against%20Hamas%20and%20the%20Gazans%20through%20massacres%2C%20a%20food%20and%20sanitary%20blockade%2C%20and%20population%20displacements%20which%20can%20only%20be%20described%20as%20genocidal%2C%20irreparable%20damage%20is%20being%20committed.%20The%20Israeli%20citizens%20who%20denounced%20the%20instrumentalisation%20of%20the%20Shoah%20(the%20Holocaust)%20and%20fought%20against%20the%20apartheid%20are%20hardly%20audible%20any%20more.%20Colonialist%20and%20nationalist%20fury%20is%20suffocating%20everything.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20truth%2C%20there%20is%20only%20one%20possible%20outcome%3A%20it%20is%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20so-called%20international%20community%20and%20the%20authorities%20with%20which%20it%20is%20theoretically%20endowed%2C%20demanding%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%2C%20the%20release%20of%20the%20hostages%2C%20the%20prosecution%20of%20the%20war%20crimes%20committed%20by%20both%20sides%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20countless%20UN%20resolutions%20that%20have%20gone%20unheeded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20is%20no%20chance%20of%20this%20happening.%20These%20institutions%20have%20been%20neutralised%20by%20the%20major%20or%20medium-sized%20imperialist%20powers%2C%20and%20the%20Jewish-Arab%20conflict%20has%20once%20again%20become%20an%20issue%20in%20the%20manoeuvres%20they%20engage%20in%20to%20determine%20spheres%20of%20influence%20and%20networks%20of%20alliances%2C%20in%20a%20context%20of%20cold%20and%20hot%20wars.%20%E2%80%9CGeopolitical%E2%80%9D%20strategies%20and%20their%20regional%20projections%20obliterate%20any%20effective%20international%20legality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20in%20a%20circle%20of%20impotence%20and%20calculation%20from%20which%20there%20is%20no%20escape.%20The%20catastrophe%20will%20therefore%20carry%20to%20term%2C%20and%20we%20will%20suffer%20the%20consequences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E*Rabin%20was%20assassinated%20on%20November%204%2C%201994%20by%20the%20Zionist%20terrorist%20Yigal%20Amir%20who%20was%20opposed%20to%20the%20peace%20process.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20(in%20English%20translation%20by%20Ma%C3%ABl%20Mont%C3%A9vil)%20was%20first%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.philosophy-world-democracy.org%2Farticles-1%2Ftill-death-palestine%5C%22%3EPhilosophy%20World%20Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C3%89tienne%C2%A0Balibar%C2%A0is%20a%20French%20philosopher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698658205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14144837%2FF8Ujv0qWkAA5W3q.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%