mmigration%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20highlighted%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20Indian%20migrants%20illegally%20crossing%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDiego%20Pi%C3%B1a%20Lopez%2C%20director%20of%20Casa%20Alitas%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20helps%20migrants%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EWSJ%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20his%20shelter%20has%20had%20to%20rethink%20dietary%20restrictions%20and%20consider%20religious%20and%20cultural%20differences%2C%20given%20the%20large%20number%20of%20Indian%20migrants%20they%20are%20now%20seeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20used%20to%20be%20an%20annual%20thing%20that%20in%20the%20summers%20we%20would%20see%20small%20pockets%20of%20people%20coming%20from%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20are%20seeing%20people%20from%20India%20almost%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Ahluwalia%2C%20an%20immigration%20lawyer%20who%20is%20representing%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20compelled%20to%20leave%20India%20after%20he%20was%20threatened%20by%20men%20allegedly%20affiliated%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20WSJ%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20he%E2%80%99s%20seeing%20an%20increasing%20number%20of%20political%20and%20religious%20persecution%20asylum%20cases%20from%20India%2C%20with%20a%20notable%20rise%20within%20the%20Sikh%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20for%20Indians%20illegally%20migrating%20to%20the%20US%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20economic%20opportunities%E2%80%9D%20in%20their%20own%20country%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698656417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30134642%2Fimage-1455.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Freligious-persecution-lack-of-jobs-a-record-number-of-indians-are-illegally-crossing-the-us-border%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%2042%2C000%20migrants%20from%20India%20have%20crossed%20the%20southern%20border%20illegally%