2037%20to%2038%20seconds%20apart%2C%20hit%20the%20spot%20where%20a%20group%20of%20seven%20journalists%20had%20been%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%20The%20first%20killed%C2%A0%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20photojournalist%20Issam%20Abdallah%2C%20according%20to%20his%20colleagues%20who%20were%20with%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20RSF%20has%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20second%2C%20more%20powerful%20strike%2C%20with%20a%20payload%20of%20more%20than%203%20kg%20TNT%20equivalent%20according%20to%20RSF%E2%80%99s%20ballistic%20expertise%2C%20ignited%20the%20Al%20Jazeera%20vehicle%2C%20a%20white%20Toyota%2C%20next%20to%20which%20the%20reporter%20was%20standing%2C%20injuring%20Al%20Jazeera%20journalists%20Carmen%20Joukhadar%20and%20Elie%20Brakhya%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20AFP%20colleague%20Dylan%20Collins.%20The%20strike%20displaced%20the%20vehicle%20by%20around%2090%20degrees%20from%20its%20original%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20RSF%20says%20it%20has%20determined%20that%20the%20shots%20came%20from%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Israeli%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20strikes%20in%20the%20same%20place%20in%20such%20a%20short%20space%20of%20time%20(just%20over%2030%20seconds)%2C%20from%20the%20same%20direction%2C%20clearly%20indicate%20precise%20targeting%2C%E2%80%9D%20RSF%20noted.%20The%20group%20added%20that%20it%20is%20unlikely%20the%20journalists%20were%20mistaken%20for%20combatants%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20were%20not%20hiding%3A%20in%20order%20to%20have%20a%20clear%20field%20of%20vision%2C%20they%20had%20been%20in%20the%20open%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20on%20the%20top%20of%20a%20hill.%20They%20were%20wearing%20helmets%20and%20bullet-proof%20waistcoats%20marked%20%E2%80%9Cpress%E2%80%9D.%20Their%20car%20was%20also%20identified%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpress%E2%80%9D%20thanks%20to%20a%20marking%20on%20the%20roof%2C%20according%20to%20witnesses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20RSF%20notes%2C%20an%20Israeli%20helicopter%20had%20flown%20over%20the%20vicinity%20and%20so%20knew%20that%20journalists%20were%20stationed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpj.org%2F2023%2F10%2Fjournalist-casualties-in-the-israel-gaza-conflict%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2029%20journalists%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20violence%20so%20far.%20Of%20those%20killed%2C%2024%20are%20Palestinian%2C%20four%20Israeli%20and%20one%20Lebanese.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20released%20after%20the%20RSF%20made%20its%20findings%20public%2C%20Reuters%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20reviewing%20the%20preliminary%20conclusion%20reached%20by%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%20(RSF)%2C%20which%20found%20that%20Issam%20Abdallah%20and%20other%20journalists%20in%20Alma%20el-Chaab%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20deliberately%20fired%20upon%20from%20the%20direction%20of%20Israel%20on%2013%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-6%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20reiterate%20our%20call%20to%20the%20Israeli%20authorities%20to%20conduct%20a%20swift%2C%20thorough%20and%20transparent%20probe%20into%20what%20happened.%20And%20we%20call%20upon%20all%20other%20authorities%20with%20information%20about%20the%20incident%20to%20provide%20it.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20journalists%20to%20report%20the%20news%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20free%20of%20harassment%20or%20harm%2C%20wherever%20they%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698655510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30141339%2FF8VvWPgWcAAEdev.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fpress-vehicle-targeted-at-israel-lebanon-border-incident-that-killed-reuters-reporter-rsf%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Significantly%2C%20RSF%20says%20it%20has%20determined%20that%20the%20shots%20came%20from%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Israeli%20border.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fpress-vehicle-targeted-at-israel-lebanon-border-incident-that-killed-reuters-reporter-rsf%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Gehlot%20Ji%20Is%20Chief%20Minister%20Number%201%20But...'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03172641%2FGehlot-JPG.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20absence%20of%20a%20pan-Rajasthan%20leader%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20with%20the%20party%20lacking%20clarity%20over%20the%20role%20assigned%20to%20former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhra%20Raje%2C%20has%20ensured%20the%20high-stakes%20battle%20for%20Rajasthan%20pits%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20directly%20against%20Modi.%20Given%20that%20a%20prime%20minister%20is%20hardly%20ever%20under%20scrutiny%20in%20a%20state%20election%2C%20the%20campaign%20in%20the%20state%20centres%20around%20how%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20record%20and%20personality%20are%20perceived.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22248%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGehlot%E2%80%99s%20record%20in%20governance%2C%20as%20even%20his%20opponents%20grudgingly%20concede%2C%20is%20largely%20praiseworthy.%20Even%20the%20more%20critical%20adjectives%20reserved%20for%20him%20%E2%80%93%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwily%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cshrewd%20politician%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20are%2C%20at%20best%2C%20mild.%C2%A0%20Yet%2C%20this%20record%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20assure%20the%20Congress%20electoral%20victory%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20many%20ifs%20and%20buts%2C%20some%20very%20peculiar%20to%20Rajasthan%2C%20that%20crop%20up%20in%20this%20campaign.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20turn%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnti-incumbency%20is%20a%20given%20in%20most%20states%20but%20widely%20used%20terms%20such%20as%20revolving%20door%20or%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eroti%20palatna%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20indicate%20that%20Rajasthan%20politics%20has%20created%20a%20dynamic%20of%20its%20own.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGehlot%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eji%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20done%20good%20work%20for%20the%20state%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20doubt%20about%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vikas%20Sethia%20told%20me%20as%20he%20fed%20pigeons%20at%20the%20Sanganeri%20Darwaza%2C%20one%20of%20Jaipur%E2%80%99s%20famed%20gates%20leading%20into%20the%20old%20city.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20is%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebaari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(turn)%20to%20come%20to%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20a%20formulation%20that%20gives%20no%20insight%20into%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20politics%2C%20merely%20into%20the%20history%20of%20electoral%20results.%20Since%201998%2C%20when%20Gehlot%20first%20swept%20into%20power%2C%20with%20153%20out%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20200%20seats%2C%20no%20incumbent%20party%20has%20ever%20won%20a%20second%20term.%20For%20the%20past%2025%20years%20and%20five%20elections%2C%20Gehlot%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Vasundhra%20Raje%20Scindia%20have%20taken%20turns%20to%20wield%20power%2C%20leaving%20the%20state%20accustomed%20to%20voting%20out%20incumbent%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20happy%20with%20Gehlot%20ji%20once%20and%20then%20Vasundhra%20ji.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20democratic%20tradition%2C%20we%20must%20follow%20it%20as%20it%20has%20worked%20for%20Rajasthan%2C%20%E2%80%9Csays%20Ramesh%20Mittal%2C%20a%20trader%20at%20Johari%20Bazaar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20those%20who%20are%20not%20naturally%20inclined%20to%20this%20formulation%20bring%20it%20up%20even%20in%20the%20most%20cursory%20of%20conversations.%20This%20is%20true%20from%20the%20palaces%20of%20the%20state%20to%20its%20streets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26144739%2FF9WlVtnaYAAHc5Y.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26144739%2FF9WlVtnaYAAHc5Y.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26144739%2FF9WlVtnaYAAHc5Y-300x176.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26144739%2FF9WlVtnaYAAHc5Y-1024x601.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26144739%2FF9WlVtnaYAAHc5Y-425x250.jpeg%20425w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681832%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22704%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20addressing%20the%20press.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40ashokgehlot51%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHari%20Bairwa%2C%20who%20sells%20accessories%20from%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethela%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(cart)%20near%20Bedi%20Chaupr%2C%20said%20%E2%80%9CThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20cricket%20game%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekee%20ab%20kis%20kee%20batting%20kee%20baari%20aayegee%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(who%E2%80%99s%20turn%20to%20bat%20now%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20changing%20a%20government%20just%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20done%20for%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20century%20is%20stupid.%20It%20ignores%20the%20development%20Gehlot%20has%20done%20for%20the%20poor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20luxury%20of%20such%20a%20choice%20is%20not%20available%20to%20the%20Muslims.%20In%20his%20mid-seventies%2C%20Ajmal%20Lateef%2C%20whose%20family%20has%20traditionally%20been%20working%20in%20the%20Jaipuri%20quilt%20industry%2C%20has%20seen%20many%20changes%20in%20his%20constituency%20%E2%80%93%20Hawa%20Mahal.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20Bhairon%20Singh%20ji%E2%80%99s%20BJP%2C%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20even%20Vasundhra%E2%80%99s%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20BJP.%20They%20are%20still%20not%20giving%20her%20the%20post%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20even%20though%20BJP%20voters%20are%20asking%20for%20it.%20No%20Muslim%20can%20think%20of%20just%20roti%20palatna%20for%20the%20sake%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Epalatna%2C%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20lose.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20has%20sensed%20the%20increased%20polarisation%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20charged%20rhetoric%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20fielded%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20Hawa%20Mahal%20constituency.%20As%20is%20always%20the%20case%20with%20the%20AIMIM%2C%20this%20has%20only%20served%20to%20increase%20speculation%20over%20who%20gains%20from%20such%20a%20move.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CCM%20number%20one%20but%20the%20Gujjars%20are%20upset%20with%20him%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESitting%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20a%20sweet-shop%20near%20the%20Mihir%20Bhoj%20Chowk%20at%20Bhandarej%20village%2C%20just%20off%20the%20new%20Dausa-Delhi%20highway%2C%20Hargovind%20Gujjar%20was%20dwelling%20on%20the%20history%20of%20his%20village%20before%20he%20stopped%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CGehlot%20ji%20is%20the%20best%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20work%20he%E2%80%99s%20done%2C%20the%20CM%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edum.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EBu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Et%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20they%20messed%20up%20with%20%5BSachin%5D%20Pilot%2C%20they%20took%20our%20votes%20saying%20Pilot%20will%20be%20CM.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Hargovind%20explained%2C%20the%20community%20also%20felt%20that%20Pilot%20was%20humiliated%20so%20%E2%80%9C90%25%20of%20the%20Gujjar%20vote%20will%20not%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20before%20reiterating%20that%20Gehlot%20is%20the%20best%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDausa%20was%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Gujjar%20agitation%20in%202008%20when%20the%20community%20was%20demanding%20ST%20reservations.%20Their%20anger%20at%20the%20time%20was%20directed%20against%20Vasundhra%2C%20then%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27135056%2FF9C5a33XkAA9juX.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27135056%2FF9C5a33XkAA9juX.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27135056%2FF9C5a33XkAA9juX-300x170.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27135056%2FF9C5a33XkAA9juX-1024x580.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682029%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESachin%20Pilot.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40SachinPilot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20BJP%20was%20able%20to%20consolidate%20their%20vote%20after%20she%20promised%20them%20reservations.%20The%20man%20who%20led%20the%20Gujjar%20agitation%2C%20Kirori%20Singh%20Bainsla%2C%20fought%20the%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Tonk-Sawai%20Madhopur%20constituency%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket.%20It%20was%20only%20in%202018%2C%20with%20Pilot%20as%20Congress%20state%20president%2C%20that%20the%20Gujjars%20returned%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Gujjars%20are%20a%20decisive%20factor%20in%2010%20to%2015%20seats%20but%20wield%20influence%20over%2040%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20is%20evoking%20its%20legacy%20among%20the%20community%20by%20fielding%20late%20Gurjar%20leader%20Kirori%20Singh%20Bainsla%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Vijay%2C%20from%20Deoli-Uniara%20in%20Tonk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20also%20imported%20the%20communal%20rhetoric%20that%20has%20worked%20for%20it%20among%20the%20Gujjars%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20has%20even%20deputed%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%2C%20the%20MP%20who%20had%20recently%20used%20abusive%20language%20against%20a%20Muslim%20MP%20from%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20for%20election%20duty%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20Congress%20leaders%20do%20not%20see%20the%20Gujjar%20vote%20as%20a%20lost%20cause.%20Pilot%2C%20they%20say%2C%20has%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20ticket%20distribution%20in%20this%20area%20and%20his%20impact%20could%20be%20great.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHargovind%20conceded%20as%20much%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Sachin%20Pilot%20gives%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eishaara%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(indication)%20then%20all%20the%20Gujjars%20will%20once%20again%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20287px)%2085vw%2C%20287px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30113307%2FF6ofEoJbAAAe0yh-225x300.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22287%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30113307%2FF6ofEoJbAAAe0yh-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30113307%2FF6ofEoJbAAAe0yh.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22383%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKirori%20Lal%20Meena.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40DrKirodilalBJP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20battle%20over%20the%20Gujjar%20vote%20is%20only%20one%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20bid%20by%20both%20parties%20to%20attract%20different%20castes%20and%20communities.%20If%20the%20Gujjar%20vote%20goes%20one%20way%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20Meenas%2C%20who%20had%20strongly%20resisted%20the%20Gujjar%20claim%20to%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20reservation%2C%20will%20go%20the%20other%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20aggressively%20pushing%20its%20local%20leader%20Kirori%20Lal%20Meena%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20face%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%20The%20party%20has%20been%20working%20on%20the%20calculation%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20lose%20the%20Gujjar%20vote%20while%20the%20BJP%20will%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20Meena%20vote%2C%20which%20traditionally%20leans%20towards%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGehlot%20is%20himself%20from%20the%20Maali%20caste%20and%20is%20perhaps%20the%20only%20prominent%20Congress%20leader%20of%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20who%20understands%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20non-dominant%20OBC%20vote.%20It%20is%20a%20vote%20that%20could%20be%20crucial%20at%20a%20time%20when%20calculations%20focus%20on%20the%20large%20caste%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Rajputs%20and%20the%20Jats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CGehlot%20is%20honest%20but%20his%20MLAs%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20image%20remains%20largely%20intact%2C%20charges%20of%20corruption%20plague%20several%20of%20his%20incumbent%20MLAs.%20Yet%2C%20going%20against%20the%20logic%20of%20addressing%20anti-incumbency%2C%20the%20party%20has%20repeated%2076%20sitting%20MLAs%20out%20of%20the%2095%20seats%20the%20Congress%20has%20declared%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20roots%20of%20this%20compulsion%20lie%20in%20the%20problems%20Gehlot%20faced%20within%20the%20party%2C%20from%20Pilot%20and%20the%20party%20high%20command%2C%20forcing%20him%20to%20seek%20the%20support%20of%20MLAs%20whom%20he%20is%20now%20obliged%20to%20repeat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20he%20dealt%20with%20these%20problems%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20on%20the%20prowl.%20It%20was%20looking%20to%20prise%20his%20MLAs%20away%20to%20engineer%20a%20change%20in%20government%20and%20repeat%20its%20success%20in%20the%20adjoining%20state%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20was%20offering%20crores%20to%20winning%20MLAs%20to%20cross-over.%20To%20keep%20them%20with%20him%2C%20Gehlot%20ji%20gave%20them%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epoori%20chhoot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(free%20hand)%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20Gopal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20retired%20government%20employee%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20if%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20his%20analysis%20is%20dispassionate%2C%20he%20makes%20it%20clear%20he%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20pithily%20explains%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBrahman%20vote%20hoon%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(I%20am%20part%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20vote)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20ask%20him%20if%20he%20thinks%20the%20charges%20are%20genuine%2C%20he%20replies%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20go%20case%20by%20case.%20There%20are%20some%20MLAs%20who%20have%20done%20good%20work%20in%20their%20constituency%2C%20better%20than%20previous%20governments%2C%20but%20they%20are%20arrogant%20and%20their%20families%20have%20made%20money.%20That%20was%20true%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20it%20is%20true%20of%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20charges%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20successful%20in%20making%20this%20the%20narrative%20of%20these%20elections%2C%20constantly%20targeting%20the%20Congress%20on%20this%20score.%20Conveniently%20timed%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20raids%20have%20only%20seemed%20like%20an%20extension%20of%20their%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-we-know-so-far-about-congress-bjp-candidates-in-rajasthan%5C%22%3EWhat%20We%20Know%20So%20Far%20About%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20Candidates%20in%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20helped%20that%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20own%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20Pilot%2C%20went%20on%20what%20he%20called%20an%20anti-corruption%20%3Cem%3Eyatra%20%3C%2Fem%3E(march).%20The%20overt%20reason%20for%20the%20yatra%20was%20to%20charge%20Gehlot%20with%20going%20soft%20on%20corruption%20which%20took%20place%20under%20Raje%20but%20the%20subtext%20was%20not%20lost%20on%20anyone%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDinesh%20Meena%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20local%20politicians%2C%20explained%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20yatra%3A%20%E2%80%9CSome%20people%20on%20the%20ground%20thought%20Pilot%20was%20saying%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20own%20people%20are%20corrupt%2C%20at%20least%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20BJP%20workers%20went%20around%20saying.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CGehlot%E2%80%99s%20development%20programmes%20are%20great%20but%20will%20they%20reach%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0In%20September%202023%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20set%20out%20on%20a%209-day%20journey%20across%20the%20state%2C%20covering%2018%20districts%2C%20to%20publicise%20and%20strengthen%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20initiated%20by%20his%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20these%20laws%20and%20schemes%20were%20hailed%20as%20%E2%80%98pioneering%E2%80%99%2C%20like%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Shehari%20Rozgar%20Guarantee%20Yojana%2C%20which%2C%20like%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20assures%20work%20in%20urban%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20thrust%20on%20welfare%20schemes%20has%20ensured%20developmental%20issues%20are%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20electoral%20agenda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20laws%20and%20the%20schemes%20have%20been%20extensively%20branded%E2%80%93%20almost%20as%20if%20a%20leaf%20has%20been%20taken%20out%20of%20the%20Modi%20book%20of%20publicity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20though%2C%20lacks%20a%20cadre%20of%20the%20kind%20which%20allows%20the%20BJP%20to%20claim%20direct%20credit%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20schemes%2C%20whatever%20their%20actual%20impact%20on%20the%20ground.%20For%20instance%2C%20some%20among%20the%20women%20who%20had%20gathered%20near%20an%20anganwadi%20centre%20on%20Bala%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EFort%20Road%2C%20Alwar%20were%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20it%20was%20Modi%20who%20had%20given%20them%20health%20insurance.%20This%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Chiranjeevi%20health%20scheme%20in%20the%20state%20is%20one%20of%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20most%20publicised%20achievements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Balla%20Devi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20women%20at%20the%20anganwadi%20centre%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%20ji%20has%20given%20us%20free%20medicines%20and%20mobile%20phones%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20had%20to%20be%20corrected%20by%20another%20in%20the%20group%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20you%20think%20it%20is%20called%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emukhyamantri%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eyojana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20scheme)%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20for%20a%20change%20on%20the%20backfoot%20in%20this%20narrative%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evikas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(development)%2C%20has%20aggressively%20been%20trying%20to%20dismiss%20the%20schemes%20and%20yojanas%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erevadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20freebies.%20It%20has%20some%20resonance%2C%20especially%20amongst%20its%20upper%20caste%20constituency%2C%20like%20Satya%20Sharma%2C%20a%20retired%20teacher%20from%20Bassi%20who%20would%20begin%20to%20heckle%20anyone%20who%20spoke%20of%20the%20benefits%20they%E2%80%99d%20received%20from%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESitting%20next%20to%20him%2C%20two%20men%20from%20the%20Meena%20community%2C%20Dinesh%20and%20Kalyan%2C%20summed%20up%20one%20of%20the%20decisive%20differences%20between%20the%20cadre%2C%20a%20difference%20that%20that%20will%20shape%20this%20poll%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20are%20loud%20and%20their%20workers%20spread%20misinformation%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20not%20quick%20and%20cohesive%20enough%20to%20counter%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERadhika%20Bordia%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698654633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03172641%2FGehlot-JPG.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgehlot-ji-is-chief-minister-number-1-but%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20record%20in%20governance%2C%20as%20even%20his%20opponents%20grudgingly%20concede%2C%20is%20largely%20praiseworthy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgehlot-ji-is-chief-minister-number-1-but%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Denies%20Bail%20to%20Delhi%20Ex-Deputy%20CM%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20in%20Jail%20for%209%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30132930%2FFnUmsIjWAAEE9Es.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20refused%20bail%20to%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20February%20this%20year%20over%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%20which%20central%20agencies%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20are%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESisodia%20is%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20in%20opposition%20to%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20several%20high%20profile%20party%20leaders%20to%20have%20been%20held%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20in%20what%20opposition%20parties%20including%20the%20AAP%20have%20referred%20to%20as%20an%20act%20of%20political%20vendetta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-manish-sisodia-aap-bail-delhi-excise-policy-241147%5C%22%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20S.V.N.%20Bhatti%20said%20that%20while%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccertain%20aspects%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20case%20which%20the%20court%20held%20as%20doubtful%2C%20the%20one%20which%20concerns%20the%20transfer%20of%20Rs%20338%20crores%20is%20%E2%80%9Ctentatively%20established.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLegal%20questions%20have%20been%20answered%20in%20a%20limited%20way.%20In%20the%20analysis%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20aspects%2C%20which%20we%20said%20are%20doubtful.%20But%20one%20aspect%2C%20with%20regard%20to%20transfer%20of%20money%2C%20Rs%20338%20crores%2C%20is%20tentatively%20established.%20We%20have%20therefore%20dismissed%20the%20application%20for%20bail%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20was%20quoted%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20various%20points%20during%20the%20hearing%20of%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20plea%20against%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20of%20his%20bail%20pleas%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-money-has-come-to-manish-sisodia-how-will-you-bring-him-under-pmla-sc-to-ed%5C%22%3Eexpressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20doubts%20over%20the%20case.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20it%20asked%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%20as%20to%20how%20they%20seek%20to%20%E2%80%9Cestablish%20money%20laundering%20by%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20factually%20and%20legally%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20dismissing%20the%20application%20for%20bail%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%20that%2