20the%20state%20government%20in%20Bihar%20released%20a%20list%20of%20209%20castes%2C%20enumerating%20their%20names%20and%20populations%2C%20and%20their%20respective%20share%20in%20the%20total%20population.%20From%20a%20political%20perspective%2C%20it%20was%20not%20just%20a%20census%20but%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20era%20in%20politics%2C%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20Mandal%203.0.%20The%20survey%20has%20had%20a%20snowball%20effect%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20politics%2C%20as%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20conduct%20a%20caste-based%20survey%20in%20the%20state%20just%20before%20the%20election%20notification%20was%20issued.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20also%20announced%20plans%20for%20caste-based%20surveys%20in%20other%20states.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20yet%20to%20come%20up%20with%20something%20to%20counter%20this%20demand%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20neither%20able%20to%20oppose%20nor%20support%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20we%20will%20discuss%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government.%20What%20are%20the%20traditions%20of%20these%20castes%3F%20How%20far%20do%20they%20extend%20and%20what%20is%20their%20status%20today%3F%20Although%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20status%20has%20not%20been%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20we%20will%20try%20to%20uncover%20these%20layers%20within%20the%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20333px)%2085vw%2C%20333px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22333%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22477%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20let%20us%20talk%20about%20a%20caste%20which%20has%20been%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20politically%20powerful%20castes%20in%20Bihar%20since%20at%20least%201990%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Ghasi%20caste.%20It%20is%20ranked%2056%20in%20the%20report%20released%20by%20Bihar%20government%20and%20its%20total%20population%20is%20stated%20to%20be%20only%201%2C462%20people%2C%20that%20is%20only%200.0011%25%20of%20the%20total%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhasi%20is%20historically%20a%20caste%20of%20shepherds.%20Unlike%20those%20shepherds%20who%20live%20like%20nomads%20with%20their%20sheep%2C%20goats%2C%20cattle%2C%20etc.%2C%20these%20are%20shepherds%20who%20have%20settled%20down%20in%20the%20plains.%20They%20are%20also%20called%20Ghasiyaras.%20The%20name%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20word%20for%20grass%2C%20which%20hints%20to%20their%20profession%20of%20the%20past%20%E2%80%93%20to%20chop%20and%20fetch%20grass%20to%20feed%20the%20cattle.%20The%20tradition%20of%20calling%20them%20Ghasi%20may%20have%20started%20when%20a%20group%20of%20nomadic%20herders%20decided%20to%20settle%20down%20for%20a%20secure%20and%20stable%20life.%20They%20must%20have%20had%20two%20things%20before%20them.%20Firstly%2C%20their%20cattle%20get%20fodder%20and%20water%2C%20and%20secondly%20they%20get%20land%20to%20grow%20grains%20to%20sustain%20themselves.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20the%20ancestors%20of%20this%20caste%20might%20have%20adopted%20farming%20and%20cattle%20rearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20circumstances%20have%20changed%20with%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20settling%20down%20in%20the%20plains%2C%20they%20must%20have%20gradually%20lost%20their%20tribal%20identity%2C%20which%20was%20replaced%20with%20a%20non-tribal%20identity.%20Ghasis%20are%20also%20called%20Ghoshi%20and%20Goshi.%20The%20meaning%20of%20these%20two%20words%20is%20not%20clearly%20defined%20anywhere%2C%20but%20in%20Hindi%20literature%20the%20term%20Ghoshi%20refers%20to%20%E2%80%98caller%E2%80%99%2C%20derived%20from%20the%20word%20Ghosh%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98to%20call%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20Ghoshi%20means%20%E2%80%98the%20one%20who%20calls%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Bihar%2C%20this%20caste%20is%20spread%20over%20some%20areas%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20sub-caste%20of%20Yadavs.%20Many%20foreign%20historians%20%E2%80%93%20Horace%20Arthur%20Rose%2C%20Denzil%20Ibbetson%2C%20Edward%20Douglas%20MacLagan%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%93%20have%20noted%20that%20the%20caste%20has%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20members.%20Some%20historians%20believe%20that%20those%20Yadavs%20who%20converted%20to%20Islam%20were%20called%20Ghosi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20one%20believes%20this%20now.%20Now%2C%20even%20those%20who%20were%20born%20in%20Ghosi%20families%20have%20started%20calling%20themselves%20Yadav%20instead%20of%20Ghosi.%20People%20of%20this%20caste%20are%20found%2C%20if%20only%20sporadically%2C%20in%20the%20Magadha%20region%20of%20Bihar.%20They%20also%20live%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Mainpuri%2C%20Etawah%2C%20Hamirpur%2C%20Jhansi%2C%20Banda%2C%20Jalaun%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Fatehpur%20etc.%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20Indian%20Hindu%20castes%20which%20are%20divided%20into%20%3Cem%3Egotras%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Ghasi%20caste%20are%20also%20divided%20into%20many%20gotras%20and%20even%20today%20they%20do%20not%20form%20marriage%20alliances%20outside%20their%20gotras.%20Some%20of%20these%20gotras%20are%20%E2%80%93%20Babariya%20or%20Barbaiya%2C%20Phatak%2C%20Jiwariya%20or%20Jarwariya%2C%20Fatkaalu%20or%20Fatkiyan%2C%20Karaiya%2C%20Shondele%2C%20Raut%2C%20Lahugaya%2C%20Angoori%2C%20Bhrigude%20or%20Bhrigudev%2C%20Gainduya%20or%20Guduya%2C%20Nigana%20and%20Dhoomar%20or%20Dhunr%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20have%20many%20legends%20of%20their%20own%2C%20and%20in%20them%20the%20connection%20with%20Krishna%20is%20central.%20However%2C%20a%20big%20change%20has%20been%20witnessed%20now%20that%20everyone%20has%20come%20under%20the%20umbrella%20term%20Yadav.%20Therefore%2C%20no%20need%20is%20felt%20for%20a%20separate%20existence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Ghasi%20or%20Ghosi.%20There%20are%20political%20reasons%20behind%20this%2C%20too.%20The%20politics%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20have%20come%20close%20to%20uniting%20all%20Yadavs.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20they%20has%20become%20a%20big%20political%20force%20collectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Ghasi%20caste%20has%20been%20separately%20mentioned%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste-based%20survey.%20It%20means%20there%20are%20still%20some%20people%20who%20do%20not%20like%20to%20call%20themselves%20Yadav.%20They%20are%20still%20Ghasi%2C%20the%20shepherds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENawal%20Kishor%20Kumar%20is%20the%20Hindi%20editor%20of%20Forward%20Press%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698643846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30100237%2F3100990738_7598ee7b2c_o-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Who%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizens%20Have%20No%20Fundamental%20Right%20to%20Know%20of%20Source%20of%20Political%20Funding%3A%20AG%20to%20SC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAttorney%20General%20of%20India%20R.%20Venkataramani%20on%20Sunday%20(October%2029)%20submitted%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20citizens%20have%20no%20fundamental%20right%20to%20know%20the%20sources%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AG%20was%20posting%20his%20views%20on%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20opaque%20nature%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20matter%20is%20posted%20for%20hearing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud-led%20bench%20on%20October%2031.%20The%20bench%20also%20comprises%20Justices%C2%A0Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%C2%A0B.R.%20Gavai%2C%C2%A0J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%C2%A0Manoj%20Misra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVenkataramani%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20be%20entering%20the%20domain%20of%20policy%20if%20it%20tried%20to%20regulate%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20general%20right%20to%20know%20anything%20and%20everything%20without%20being%20subjected%20to%20reasonable%20restrictions.%20Secondly%2C%20the%20right%20to%20know%20as%20necessary%20for%20expression%20can%20be%20for%20specific%20ends%20or%20purposes%20and%20not%20otherwise%2C%E2%80%9D%20AG%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fcitizens-dont-have-right-to-information-regarding-funding-of-a-political-party-centre-tells-supreme-court-in-electoral-bonds-case-241137%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20just%20because%20courts%20have%20ruled%20that%20citizens%20have%20the%20right%20to%20know%20a%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20criminal%20antecedents%2C%20that%20cannot%20be%20extended%20to%20knowledge%20about%20funding%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20does%20not%20infringe%20upon%20any%20individual%E2%80%99s%20rights%2C%20the%20AG%20continued%2C%20and%20cannot%20be%20said%20to%20be%20repugnant%20to%20any%20right%20under%20Part%20III%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20scheme%20in%20question%20extends%20the%20benefit%20of%20confidentiality%20to%20the%20contributor.%20It%20ensures%20and%20promotes%20clean%20money%20being%20contributed.%20It%20ensures%20abiding%20by%20tax%20obligations.%20Thus%2C%20it%20does%20not%20fall%20foul%20of%20any%20existing%20right.%20A%20constitutional%20Court%20reviews%20State%20action%20only%20if%20it%20impinges%20upon%20existing%20rights%20and%20not%20because%20State%20action%20has%20not%20provided%20for%20a%20possible%20right%20or%20an%20expectation%20howsoever%20desirable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20petition%2C%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%2C%20challenges%20the%20Finance%20Act%2C%202017%20which%20was%20enacted%20as%20a%20money%20bill%20and%20introduced%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20electoral%20funding.%20The%20Act%20also%20removed%20the%20previous%20limit%20of%207.5%25%20of%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20average%20three-year%20net%20profit%20for%20political%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20scheme%2C%20a%20company%20is%20not%20required%20to%20name%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20which%20such%20contributions%20are%20made.%20The%20donors%E2%80%99%20names%20are%20also%20not%20revealed%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20argue%20that%20these%20amendments%20will%20result%20in%20opaqueness%2C%20heighten%20the%20odds%20of%20conflict%20of%20interest%20and%20also%20drastically%20increase%20black%20money%20and%20corruption.%20The%20petitioners%20also%20claim%20that%20this%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20shell%20companies%20and%20rise%20of%20benami%20transactions%20to%20channelise%20undocumented%20money%20into%20the%20political%20and%20electoral%20process%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2010%20during%20the%20preliminary%20hearing%2C%20counsel%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20for%20the%20petitioners%20alleged%20that%20due%20to%20non-decision%20on%20the%20matter%20by%20the%20court%20continuously%20since%202017%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20been%20enjoying%20the%20fruits%20of%20the%20scheme%20in%20every%20general%20election%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20well%20as%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20thus%20upsetting%20the%20level%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhushan%20submitted%20that%20the%20scheme%2C%20apart%20from%20having%20been%20fraudulently%20introduced%20through%20a%20money%20bill%2C%20also%20seeks%20to%20legalise%20anonymous%20sources%20of%20political%20funding.%20He%20alleged%20that%20the%20scheme%20violates%20the%20right%20to%20information%20about%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20promotes%20corruption.%20When%20a%20legislative%20measure%20is%20introduced%20by%20the%20government%20as%20a%20money%20bill%2C%20it%20does%20not%20require%20approval%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhushan%20explained%20that%20political%20parties%20received%20funds%20most%20likely%20from%20companies%20which%20received%20some%20benefit%20or%20the%20other%20from%20them.%20He%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20as%20corruption-free%20society%20is%20a%20facet%20of%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20as%20held%20by%20the%20court%2C%20source%20of%20funding%20cannot%20be%20anonymous.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%2C%20as%20the%20designated%20bank%2C%20sells%20these%20bonds%20in%20the%20denominations%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20anybody%2C%20either%20in%20cash%20or%20through%20bank%20transfers%20(bank%20account%20to%20be%20opened%20if%20there%20is%20a%20cash%20deposit)%2C%20with%20the%20source%20of%20purchase%20kept%20in%20wraps.%20While%20the%20source%20is%20known%20to%20SBI%2C%20it%20is%20obliged%20not%20to%20disclose%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDetails%20regarding%20who%20donates%20to%20which%20political%20party%20and%20what%20amount%20are%20not%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698643495000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcitizens-have-no-fundamental-right-to-know-of-source-of-political-funding-ag-to-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22R.%20Venkataramani%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20be%20entering%20the%20domain%20of%20policy%20if%20it%20tried%20to%20regulate%20electoral%20bonds.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcitizens-have-no-fundamental-right-to-know-of-source-of-political-funding-ag-to-sc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fourteen%20Die%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Train%20Collision%3B%20Second%20Rail%20Accident%20in%20October%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30103100%2FF9nrsdaaQAADaVp.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Fourteen%20people%20have%20died%20and%20over%2050%20were%20injured%20in%20a%20train%20collision%20late%20on%20October%2029%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Vizianagaram%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Visakhapatnam-Rayagada%20Passenger%20Special%20train%20collided%20with%20the%20Visakhapatnam-Palasa%20passenger%20from%20the%20rear%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fandhra-pradesh-train-accident-death-toll-rescue-ops-9005289%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%20The%20hit%20led%20to%20several%20coaches%20derailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20t